data.description: Ranch style home with some acreage located in desirable Lithia Springs on low traffic quiet road with acreage. This home currently is 4 bedrooms 2 bath and has a rocking chair front porch and deck. There is a  41x34  shop that can be used for an detached garage,RV or boat storage, workshop. The outside also features cool rustic shed with covered porch could be used for storage or guest. There is No HOA and its just minutes to Sweetwater Creek Park boat ramp. Shopping and medical close by.The well maintained  front yard has fruit trees. The house sets on a large crawl space that could be converted into a basement for addition lower level square footage. The house at 2635 Kent Dr, Lithia Springs, GA 30122is located close to interstate access to Atlanta and surrounding areas.
